Audio

aucat -o ~/Videos/name-of-the-file.wav
_________________________________________________________

Screencast

ffmpeg -f x11grab -s 1366x768 -r 15 -i $DISPLAY -c:v libx264 -preset ultrafast ~/Videos/name-of-the-file.mkv
_________________________________________________________

Webcam

ffplay -f v4l2 -noborder -video_size 320x240 -i /dev/video

Alternative video sizes...

640x360 
848x480 
320x240 (My Default)
320x180 (My Default but wider)

960x540 
1280x720 (Almost full screen)